</th>
<th style="background:#f6f9fe;padding:10px;color:#0e1e3d;">Information needs<br>
</th>
<th style="background:#f6f9fe;padding:10px;color:#0e1e3d;">Purpose of information<br>
</th>
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="padding:10px;color:#5b6b88;">
<strong>People</strong><br>
</td>
<td style="padding:10px;color:#5b6b88;">Roles responsible for asset operation, maintenance, and compliance<br>
</td>
<td style="padding:10px;color:#5b6b88;">Ensure accountability and clear ownership of information<br>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 43px;">
<td style="padding:10px;color:#5b6b88;">
<strong>Process</strong><br>
</td>
<td style="padding:10px;color:#5b6b88;">Maintenance planning, risk management, reporting, and lifecycle cost processes<br>
</td>
<td style="padding:10px;color:#5b6b88;">Support operational workflows and regulatory reporting<br>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding:10px;color:#5b6b88;">
<strong>Technology</strong><br>
</td>
<td style="padding:10px;color:#5b6b88;">Structured asset data suitable for CAFM and asset management systems<br>
</td>
<td style="padding:10px;color:#5b6b88;">Enable system integration, analysis, and long-term usability<br>
</td>
</tr>
